physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Retinal findings included: movement toward the optic disc in 7 eyes (33.3%) with RD; movement beyond the optic disc in 3 eyes (14.3%) with RD and 7 eyes (87.5%) with RFs. Uniform NFL thickening occurred in 17 of 21 eyes (81.0%) with RD.
physical_examinations.changes_over_time: NFL bundles progressed from thickening to 2 distinct bundles, and then to 1 large bundle resulting in unique RFs that differ from other folds.
